# AI-Powered Business Presentation Generator

## Problem

Business professionals need to create compelling presentations for different audiences (employees, investors, board members) with tailored messaging and data insights. Each audience requires different language, metrics, and presentation styles to effectively communicate the message.

## Solution

An AI-powered presentation generator that creates context-aware slide decks by:

- Understanding audience context and goals
- Analyzing relevant data
- Generating appropriate visualizations
- Creating compelling narratives
- Adapting messaging and metrics for each audience

## Target Users

- Busy founders
- Management consultants
- Business analysts
- Corporate executives

## Features

### 1. Initial Setup Screen

- Data source configuration
- Audience selection
- Presentation goals
- Brand guidelines input

### 2. Slide Generation

- AI-powered content creation
- Data visualization generation
- Layout optimization
- Brand consistency

### 3. Presentation Mode

- Fullscreen view
- Navigation controls
- Interactive elements
- Real-time updates

### 4. Advanced Analytics

- Data insights generation
- Market research integration
- Competitor analysis
- Performance metrics

## Technical Stack

### Frontend

- React + TypeScript
- Vite for build tooling
- Shadcn UI components
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- D3.js for visualizations
- Server-Sent Events (SSE) for real-time updates

### Backend

- FastAPI
- PostgreSQL for data storage
- Redis for message queuing
- Agent framework integration
- Google ADK for A2A implementation

## Out of Scope

- External integrations
- Deck editing capabilities
- Real-time collaboration
- Version control
